Files included in the GSB package:

browse_dialog.erl         gen_file_dialog.swr       option.erl
browse_dialog.rc          gen_file_dialog.trc       save_soft_dialog.erl
browse_dialog_ui.erl      gsb.erl                   save_soft_dialog.rc
color_editor.erl          gsb.hrl                   save_soft_dialog_ui.erl
color_editor.rc           gsb.rc                    standard.erl
color_editor_ui.erl       gsb_db.erl                standard.hrl
draw.erl                  gsb_run.erl               .toolbox
draw.hrl                  gsb_ui.erl                .option
file_dialog.erl           hierarchy.erl            
file_dialog.rc            menu.erl                  toolbox.erl
file_dialog_ui.erl        menu.hrl                  transfer.erl
gen_db.erl                menutest.rc
gen_file_dialog.erl       messages.erl

Start erlang and just use make:all([load]) to create the builder.
The builder is started with gsb:start().
Note that the .toolbox and .option must be present in the current
directory.

Enjoy !

/ Peter & Fredrik (961101)


